The fiancée of Davido’s logistic manager, Israel Dmw could not contain her joy as she got a follow from the singer on Instagram. It would be recalled that some weeks ago, Israel proposed to his girlfriend after which she received the sum of N500K gift from her boyfriend’s boss. Taking to Instagram to announce an unexpected gesture from Davido, the young lady expressed utmost joy as she gets a follow from him. Expressing the joy of the privilege, Israel DMW’s fiancée wrote, “Followed by the biggest there is @davido only one baddest put some respect on my name y’all.” While quoting Davido’s lyrics, she added, “Since I was born, happiness in my blood; de talk e many many but I know say de ma talk.” 